    "Precision axis 𝒫: how strongly brain weights incoming information (Bayesian precision).",
    "Boundary axis ℬ: clarity of self-world demarcation (Markov blanket).",
    "Temporal axis 𝒯: orientation in time (past/present/future discounting)."
